operator UK Campaign Team
submitter Ian McCrea
resources UK(40)
notes
Experiment aiming to locate substorm onset and timing by using the ESR and 
Tromso VHF radars during a tail alignment of THEMIS. The experiment uses the 
ESR in steffe mode pointing south and the VHF in tau1 mode pointing at low 
elevation to the north.
